{
  "name": "Dragon Scale Mail (Black)",
  "type": "equipment",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<p>&amp;Reference[dragon]{Dragon} scale mail is made of the scales of one kind of &amp;Reference[dragon]{dragon}. Sometimes dragons collect their cast-off scales and gift them to humanoids. Other times, hunters carefully skin and preserve the hide of a dead &amp;Reference[dragon]{dragon}. In either case, &amp;Reference[dragon]{dragon} scale mail is highly valued.</p>\n<p>While wearing this armor, you gain a +1 bonus to AC, you have advantage on saving throws against the Frightful Presence and breath weapons of dragons, and you have resistance to &amp;Reference[acid]{acid} damage.</p>\n<p>Additionally, you can focus your senses as an action to magically discern the distance and direction to the closest black &amp;Reference[dragon]{dragon} within 30 miles of you. This special action can't be used again until the next dawn.</p>\n</div>",
